reviewText: Christmas present for my 9month old grandson

Our little one's love knowing where their Thomas movies are.  They go straight for the "Thomas Blue Book".  Great little dvd folder and the movies included were top notch.  Fabulous addition for any Thomas and Friends fans.
My son loves it. Watches them over and over again.

I bought this product for my son for Christmas he loves Thomas the old version and the sgi one,i happy that it came with a case because my son is always miss placing his dvds and now they will have a home in a few weeks when he opens it.

I think this set is adorable because not only do you get three classic Thomas & Friends DVDs but you also get a carrying case!  The episodes are from 2005, 2005, and 2007 so they are older and original Thomas DVDs.  Aidan liked them, but he prefers the newer Thomas episodes in CGI animation, but he does absolutely love the case!  I think this pack would be perfect for any Thomas fan as you get a little of everything with it and for the price, you can't go wrong!
